{"tid":1495411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇可能好似墨西哥咁解散警隊再重組","createTime":"2019-08-22T05:06:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T05:16:10.000Z","uid":263438,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cff3726cbffb05b6047c94212a954de01336a629","tid":1495411,"uid":263438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:06:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20141128/s00005/1417148968225/墨西哥總統宣布改革警隊架構\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20141128%2Fs00005%2F1417148968225%2F%E5%A2%A8%E8%A5%BF%E5%93%A5%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E6%94%B9%E9%9D%A9%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A%E6%9E%B6%E6%A7%8B&d=MOEBQbH5BhSBv0g7AWUGIZIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=f4bdb4aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20141128%2Fs00005%2F1417148968225%2F%E5%A2%A8%E8%A5%BF%E5%93%A5%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E6%94%B9%E9%9D%A9%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A%E6%9E%B6%E6%A7%8B&h=1ae8bce6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20141128/s00005/1417148968225/墨西哥總統宣布改革警隊架構</a><br />\n<br />\n香港黑警濫用私刑，警黑勾結，清場時濫用暴力，打被捕示威者致斷骨等，我諗大家都極憤怒<br />\n<br />\n我見墨西哥總統响14年因為當地警隊受黑社會滲透太嚴重，而解散再重組警隊，香港可唔可以做到呢？"},{"pid":"0f035404632795c8964926148154f14c93c32476","tid":1495411,"uid":204429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:08:53.000Z","msg":"有心點會唔得"},{"pid":"e4a663b9e11c1e4f161bcdd1b65d6faeea45c875","tid":1495411,"uid":263438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:14:08.000Z","msg":"可以點做？"},{"pid":"2f4c6404176cf950dc3f583620e3047a4821cacd","tid":1495411,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:16:10.000Z","msg":"大家幾時先肯行動升級搞機場？<br />\n搞機場唔單只係搞到香港經濟，亦搞到全世界經濟<br />\n有機場巴絲亦指出，停飛一日全世界要2,3日善後<br />\n大家幾時先肯齊心搞呀？<br />\n唔係搞一日就算 係要成日搞<br />\n港共想攬炒唔志在香港蝕少少 但你覺得咁多受影響既外國公司想唔想蝕？<br />\n全世界陪葬既時候，你覺得啲大國會唔會出聲？<br />\n<br />\n重點係癱瘓機場交通，唔係塞爆機場入面<br />\n空管巴絲返唔到工，航班升降效率低左就會開始delay/cancel架喇"}]}